description: "Adapted by Theodore de Bry from an original by Willem Lodewycksz, this map has some inaccuracies e.g. the Malay Peninsula (‘Chersonese’) is completely bisected by the Muar River, leaving the southern tip of the peninsula as a separate island."
title: "Nova   tabula   insularum   Iavae,   Sumatrae,   Borneonis"
